channel.title: [RS2][750k][$5 USD] Sumilions Mining Guild Smasher
channel.description:
[center][b][size=25pt]..::Mining Guild Smasher::..
By Sumilion[/size][/b][/center]
[b]A new dawn, a new guildminer, here are the specifications :[/b]
- Flawless walking. - Multiple users can be used ! - Smooth mining, if someone else mined it away, it will move on. - Mines Mith as well, once it sees it, it wont stop mining it until its gone :D - AntiBan (at choice) - AntiRandoms from SRL, guaranteed to be good. - Nice progress reporter - AutoColored!! For all you lazy peeps out there, no need to fill it in ! - Easy to use forms, if you still don't understand them ill be more than happy to explain. - Very own openbank procedures, never failed me and i've tried to make it fail ;) - Improved Anti-gas!! (had complaints about it :S) - Attaches Paxe-head when it flies off ! (not 100%) - In the slight chance that the paxe will be lost, it will get the best paxe there is from the bank
Need a powerminer to go along with ? Sure, i made one :), if you buy the guildminer youll get it from me directly.
If that doesn't blow you off your horses then it beats the hell out of me :)
[b]Reasons to trust me :[/b]
- Well im your friendly visitor from outa space! XD - Im an SRL developer, that means i cant have bad rep ;)
[b]What do i provide ?[/b]
- The script, duhuh - Authentication information - Full detail on how the form works - Full assistence with getting it to work - Full updates, i dont keep anything private from you - Free powerminer !!
[b]How the paying goes ? [/b] - You pay me 750k or 5$ through paypal - I send you the script and the authentication.
[b]How does it go after that ?[/b]
- I explain how it works ... - You have FUN!
[b]A proggie i got a few days ago :[/b]
[code]<============= Guild Slammer ==============> <========= -0.24- Progress Report =========> /==========================================\ Worked for 16 Hours, 15 Minutes and 40 Seconds Banked 119 loads[s]. Mined 2970 ores. Received 21 gems. \==========================================/[/code]
[b]Known bugs :[/b] - Gas detection ( not 100% according to some people ) - Pickaxe head detection (same as above) - Sometimes it walks to far to the north in the guild, but it usually got out of there for me.
[b]Forms :[/b] A classy script must have nice forms to go along with it ! Here they are, there are a total of three forms which open when you press a certain button. Form 1 (always pops up), [IMG]http://img329.imageshack.us/img329/2848/form1dw3.jpg[/img]
Form 2 (opens when pressing Settings on form 1) [IMG]http://img329.imageshack.us/img329/8739/form2bj7.jpg[/img]
Form 3 (opens when pressing Extra Settings on form 2) [IMG]http://img329.imageshack.us/img329/8236/form3dx5.jpg[/img]
In total i made around the 25k coal with this script so far and 1 ban.
[center][b][size=25pt]Way of contact ! :[/size][/b][/center]
You mail me / contact me on msn on the following address :
Sumilion@live.nl
Im not adding anyone, you add me ...
[b]Number of completed sales so far : 60+[/b]
